    "image_with_text_overlay_qFzrUn": {
      "type": "image-with-text-overlay",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_gyaxKJ": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "10 years. full throttle.",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_Kz6Y9x": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From day one, we've been driven by the things that connect all anglers - early mornings, long days, gas station sandwiches, the thrill of feeling that thump and the line going tight, small town bbq stops, the flash of a wake or tail that forced a quick cast, the hat backward run to the next spot, cracking a cold one at the dock, telling stories around firepit late into the night ... we've built our life around this. <br\/><br\/>More than allegiance to a species, body of water, or type of gear, we stand by the belief that life is more epic on the water. <\/p>",
            "description_size": "small"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_gyaxKJ",
        "text_Kz6Y9x"
      ],
