        "main-heading-text": "A BRIEF HISTORY",
        "tagline-text": "",
        "description-text": "<p>What started as a shirt program with our best-selling Icon, has become the ultimate hot weather fishing kit with head-to-toe coverage, in peak performance fabrics.<\/p>",
        "intro-text": "before Icon",
        "intro-description": "<p>Everything was made of cotton or fit like a trash bag and people got sweaty and sunburned.<\/p>",
