    "4741272f-d447-433a-bf7a-8df7997a0032": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "template--17918040834330__4741272f-d447-433a-bf7a-8df7997a0032-16769789110686510d-0": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rectangle_107.png",
            "image_full_width": false,
            "image_link": "",
            "title": "For All Anglers",
            "text": "<p>At Huk we are not bound by a body of water, species of fish, or type of tackle. Our life centers around finding our way to the water - we just love to fish ... so don't be shy with those invites.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "template--17918040834330__4741272f-d447-433a-bf7a-8df7997a0032-16769789110686510d-1": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rectangle_108.png",
            "image_full_width": false,
            "image_link": "",
            "title": "Everything Performs",
            "text": "<p>Our approach to everything we make starts with looking good and adding value through performance. Whether it's a technical shirt that allows you to stay out longer and cast easier or that shirt comfortable enough to pick the table on the patio when everyone else is scrambling for AC, we take a performance first approach to looking good on and off the water. <\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "template--17918040834330__4741272f-d447-433a-bf7a-8df7997a0032-16769789110686510d-2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rectangle_109.png",
            "image_full_width": false,
            "image_link": "",
            "title": "Bring The Energy",
            "text": "<p>We believe life should be epic and living your life on the water is the best way to do that. Our personality is a reflection of our team ... we love bright colors, big adventure, hookset celebrations, making faces for the camera and showing up with a case of Modelo. The water keeps us young (even if only at heart). <\/p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
